description:
TAX ASSISTANCE 2018: No income guideline. Providing income tax preparation services 2/1-4/14. Prepares both federal and state tax forms; offers E-filing at all locations. VITA Tax Locator, 800-906-9887.

Ray of Hope Baptist Church
3000 Parkside Drive, Baltimore, MD 21214. Call 410-254-3797
Provides assistance from 2/3-3/24. Walk-in Sat, 9AM-12PM. Now closed.

Coppin State University 
2500 West North Avenue, College of Business, Health and Human Service Building (HHSB), Room 108, Baltimore, MD 21216. Located off of West North Avenue connecting to the elevator stair tower, near the McDonald Child Development Center (MCDS) and the South Quad. Call 410-951-3444.
Provides assistance from 2/2-4/14. Walk-in Mon, Wed, and Fri, 12:00PM-4:30PM & Sat, 10AM-2PM (Closed on university holidays).

Must bring the following:
-- Valid photo ID for self and spouse.
-- A Social Security card for EACH family member.
-- W-2 forms for all jobs worked in the previous year.
-- Child care provider - name, address and tax ID number.
-- All banking account information (a voided check and/or savings deposit slip).
-- A copy of last year's tax return.
-- Any document or information about money received from the IRS, including the advanced Child Tax Credit.
-- All 1099 forms for other income, if any.
-- Any other tax related documents.
name: United States Department of the Treasury
